  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to describe the patient population treated and the real-life patients'
      experiences with Xamiol®gel in the long term, up to 52 weeks management of body psoriasis
      vulgaris in Russia. The result will increase the knowledge on Xamiol®gel enabling
      dermatologists and patients to optimize its use in the long term management of psoriasis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
